text: Viktor Kalinin (born 19 March 1940) is a Russian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tambov
